caption.text:
Hi! I'm Inara as Head of Judges of The 8th Business Law Competition Piala Hafni Sjahruddin, welcome you to be a part of the Biggest Business Law Competition in Indonesia!

The 8th Business Law Competition Piala Hafni Sjahruddin, is the competition held by Business Law Society Fakultas Hukum Univesitas Indonesia that encourages university students all over Indonesia to join to test their skills on Business Law which includes contract drafting, legal opinion, debate, and battle of brains.

Why?
Because The 8th BLC won't only give you the chance to work and manage one of the Biggest Business Law Competition, but it's also a medium where you can learn about the basics Business Law.

Now, become a part of us, a part of something great, something that comes only once every year.

#BLC2017
